headline: Morgan Stanley Downgrades Centene Corporation (CNC) to Equal Weight From Overweight
summary: Centene Corporation (NYSE:CNC) is one of the best cheap stocks with huge upside potential. On July 10, Morgan Stanley downgraded Centene Corporation (NYSE:CNC) to Equal Weight from Overweight, bringing the price target down to $33 from $70. The firm told investors in a research note that unexpected near-term challenges are currently outweighing the long-term upside […]
